# Flask-Rips

Flask-Rips help you build minimal REST API with resource routing.

## User Guide

Forked from [Flask-Restful](https://github.com/flask-restful/flask-restful).

You'll find the user guide just in documentation of [Flask-Restful](https://flask-restful.readthedocs.io/), but without error handlingï¼Œmarshaling, argument parsing and Data Formatting features.

